---

<BaseLayout>
  <header class="site-header u-container" data-reveal>
    <div class="site-header__brand">
      <span class="u-pill">Shyam Ajudia</span>
      <p>
        Scientist-turned DevOps engineer translating bench workflows into
        resilient cloud systems
