          Roles span academic research, biotechnology, and healthcare IT. Each
          position strengthened the bridge between scientific discovery and
          scalable technical implementation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="u-container experience">
        {
          experiences.map((job) => (
            <article class="experience__item">
              <header>
                <h3>{job.role}</h3>
                <p>{job.org}</p>
                <span>{job.years}</span>
              </header>
              <p>{job.focus}</p>
              <ul>
                {job.impact.map((item) => (
                  <li>{item}</li>
